This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and information retrieval to combat fake news. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves retrieving relevant fact checks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it deals with social media and online news. It may also fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it addresses the societal impact of fake news. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it involves verifying the veracity of information.
